are on common\nstock. Heretofore 81.50 has been tho\nquarterly dividend.\nWork of rebuilding on the site at the\ncorner of R.qton avenue and Second\nstreet, Trinidad, which was destroyed\nby fire last summer, is progressing.\nThe first, floor of the building will bo\n65x140 feet in dimensions, with a room\non tho second floor 4\u00b0xloo feet.\nThe family of a. former city official\nof Trinidad, who Is charged with hav\ning been guilty of peculations from tho\ncity funds, ha* raised B*l7 with which\nto make g\u00bb>o<l .my losses and prescrx o\nj tho family honor.","height":"19536","width":"15632"}}
